Package: sportyR
Title: Plot Scaled 'ggplot' Representations of Sports Playing Surfaces
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("Ross", "Drucker", email = "ross.a.drucker@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ross Drucker <ross.a.drucker@gmail.com>
Description: Create scaled 'ggplot' representations of playing surfaces.
    Playing surfaces are drawn pursuant to rule-book specifications.
    This package should be used as a baseline plot for displaying player
    tracking data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Imports: ggplot2, glue, dplyr
Depends: R (>= 3.3)
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), vdiffr (>= 0.3.3), roxygen2
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/rossdrucker/sportyR
BugReports: https://github.com/rossdrucker/sportyR/issues
NeedsCompilation: no
